The Neurochemistry Playbook

Reward Architecture for Feminization Practice

A system for distributed pleasure, neural rewiring, and identity capture

Part 1: Neurochemical Foundations

The goal is not to manufacture motivation through willpower. The goal is
to restructure your reward circuitry so that feminization practice
*becomes* the reward. This requires understanding four neurochemicals
and how to deliberately activate each.

