                                               content, guided sessions

  Tier 3 (Premium)  7+ day streak OR level-up  Advanced hypno, custom
                                               content, longer sessions

  Tier 4 (Vault)    Monthly milestones only    \"Black box\" content,
                                               surprises, rare material
